# How to Install Sass

This document outlines the steps taken to install Sass using npm.

## 1. Install Node.js and npm

- Go to [https://nodejs.org/](https://nodejs.org/)
- Download and install the **LTS** version of Node.js (it includes npm)

## 2. Initialize a Project (Optional)

Open your terminal or command prompt and run:

```bash
cd your-project-folder
npm init -y
#3. Install Sass Using npm
